    f"11. If the issue remains unresolved, appears account-specific, requires live reproduction, or looks like a plausible active security problem after this pre-triage, state that human help is needed and include the tag '{config.HUMAN_HANDOFF_TAG_PLACEHOLDER}'.\n\n"

    "# Rules\n"
